<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025-08-15-black-and-white.png" alt="macleod chess problem" width="382" height="388" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-71496" srcset="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025-08-15-black-and-white.png 382w, https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/2025-08-15-black-and-white-300x305.png 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 382px) 100vw, 382px" /></p>
<p>By N.A. Macleod. White to mate in two moves.</p>

